bio: Eugen is an experienced developer  with a demonstrated history of working in the management consulting industry. He is skilled in Big Data (Apache/Cloudera Stack), Scala and Java Enterprise Development. He is also a strong engineering professional with a proven record of getting new projects off the ground as well as bringing them back from the dead. He also started his career path here in Craiova.
